OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAlmost half of family      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcourts to allow reporting  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A pilot scheme to allow journalists and
OL,6, legal bloggers to report cases from    
OL,7, three family courts in England and     
OL,8, Wales is to be extended to almost half 
OL,9, of the courts in the countries.        
OL,11,FFrom 29 January, coverage of cases at  
OL,12,F16 more family court centres in England
OL,13,Fwill be permitted.                     
OL,15,FThis means 19 of the 43 centres in     
OL,16,FEngland and Wales will be part of the  
OL,17,FTransparency Pilot.                    
OL,19,FFamilies and individual social workers 
OL,20,Fwill be anonymous under the scheme.    
